The Hitch-Hiker's Guide to the Galaxy TV Theme Music is a vinyl which was released in 1980 by Original Records. It is a 7" record with four tracks.Tracks
A-side:
 The Hitch-Hiker's Guide to the Galaxy Theme Music- Journey of the Sorcerer 
B-side
 Reg Nullify in Concert
 Disaster Area - Narration
 Disaster Area- Only the End of the World Again
